      <title>拉尔夫·劳伦 (Ralph Lauren) 乘着强劲的假日需求和中国市场反弹，公布了乐观的业绩</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ralph-lauren-tops-quarterly-sales-estimate-strong-demand-2024-02-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，拉尔夫·劳伦 (Ralph Lauren) 的利润连续第 14 个季度超出预期，原因是美国对其昂贵的羊绒毛衣、外套和鸡尾酒会礼服的强劲假期需求以及中国市场的反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ralph-lauren-tops-quarterly-sales-estimate-strong-demand-2024-02-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 13:05:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
